      "symbol": "The Quietus as seal accessed through embodied trust / body-as-knowledge",
      "linkedTheme": "TP-1: Trust as structural failure — The seal can only be reached through kinetic memory, knowledge held in the body rather than mind. Trust requires the body, not just intention. Surrender must be physical.",
